casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Carter, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Carter, 120 Ohio St.3d 1201, 2008-Ohio-5365.]

(No. 2008-0085 Submitted October 14, 2008 Decided October 22, 2008.)

{¶ 1} The cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently accepted.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur. *1202Julia R. Bates, Lucas County Prosecuting Attorney, and Michael E. Narges, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee. Jeffrey P. Nunnari, for appellant.
